		(property "Description" "The MC14051B, MC14052B, and MC14053B analog multiplexersare digitally−controlled analog switches. The MC14051B effectivelyimplements an SP8T solid state switch, the MC14052B a DP4T, andthe MC14053B a Triple SPDT. All three devices feature low ONimpedance and very low OFF leakage current. Control of analogsignals up to the complete supply voltage range can be achieved."
			(at 0 0 90)
